{"tid":850120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[你大我呀]回應馬凱不獲續證　邱騰華指不擔心動搖外國投資者信心","createTime":"2018-10-06T08:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T09:45:05.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0624dab3fe17ccdb4a5d0e2f24ef5257ebd64b7b","tid":850120,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T08:25:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421615-20181006.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421615-20181006.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZJAL25VI0YkJZqPsohePU26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=de78abb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421615-20181006.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=af146680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421615-20181006.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港外國記者會副主席、金融時報亞洲新聞編輯馬凱，不獲特區政府續發工作簽證。商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華指，不擔心事件會動搖外國投資者對香港的信心。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華出席一個活動後指，對有關當局的入境決定，不方便評論，但香港從來都歡迎國際組織和商貿人士來港，在商貿、文化、旅遊，以至新聞方面都非常開放和接納，相信香港一貫的精神會繼續存在。<br />\n<br />\n另外，邱騰華表示，對於美國與加拿大達成新的貿易協定，與墨西哥組成「美墨加協議」，取代「北美自由貿易協定」後，是否能夠逐步建立更開放的自由貿易，還是固步自封，仍要觀察。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係恭喜你呀"},{"pid":"d7b71dd58a09fad9d01804303b443bda01241600","tid":850120,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T08:27:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"535941f520e6bfc475b08dd335f8e48853e8e24f","tid":850120,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"真係唔撚識架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係恭喜你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82608f45f4279ba400f4368dbcc8188af91c9be5","tid":850120,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T08:28:42.000Z","msg":